<h2 id="_2-reentrantlock-与可重入锁" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-reentrantlock-与可重入锁"><span>2. <strong><code v-pre>ReentrantLock</code> 与可重入锁</strong></span></a></h2>
